news.title: Akzo Nobel expects core profit below $146.73 million in Q4 2022
news.para: The Amsterdam-based group said it expects a core profit below 150 million euros ($146.73 million) for the fourth quarter after posting 201 million in the third quarter and 209 million euros in the fourth quarter last year.

news.title: Housing starts fall, building permits rise in USA in September 2022
news.para: Housing starts dropped 8.1% to a seasonally adjusted annual rate of 1.439 million units last month. Data for August was revised down to a rate of 1.566 million units from the previously reported 1.575 million units.

news.title: Rental searches increased 29%, listings declined 12.6% in 13 cites in Q3 2022: Magicbricks
news.para: Magicbricks.com is owned by Magicbricks Realty Services, which is a subsidiary of Times Internet.
